## What does Ruler Analytics do best?

Before switching, acknowledge Ruler Analytics' strengths:

| Strength | Why It Matters |
|----------|----------------|
| **Integrated call + web tracking** | Single tool for calls, forms, and web visits |
| **First-party cookie focus** | Privacy-conscious approach |
| **CRM closed-loop** | Revenue attribution, not just leads |
| **Offline touchpoints** | Tracks in-person events |
| **SMB-friendly** | Right-sized for smaller businesses |

If you're an SMB service business wanting simple, integrated call + web attribution, Ruler Analytics remains solid.

